title: The Little Chihuahua
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast-casual Mexican restaurant with a focus on local and sustainable ingredients. Vegan options include guacamole enchilada, tofu burrito/taco, and a black bean and fried plantain burrito. Vegan options are not specifically noted on the menu, so you have to ask for vegetarian with no cheese or sour cream. Employees are knowledgeable about vegan and vegetarian needs.
